 Association：How much does it cost to raise a child from 0 to 18 years old.</p><p style="outline: 0px;">[50]&nbsp; &nbsp;https://observatorial.com/news/economy/29428/how-much-does-it-cost-to-keep-a-child-from-0-to-18-years-old/</p><p style="outline: 0px;">[51]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ministry of Health &amp; Welfare：The high price of raising a well-educated child.</p><p style="outline: 0px;">[52]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2013/04/10/socialAffairs/The-high-price-of-raising-a-welleducated-child/2969998.html</p></div><p><br></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="10000"></mp-style-type></p>]]></summary>
