mportant;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration: none solid rgb(0, 0, 0);">2022年6月17日，泽平宏观与北京广播电视台的点燃希望首场年中秀“中国经济的十大预言”——台网累计超2000万观看，触达3亿人群。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;">2022年12月20日，由<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">泽平</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">宏观、</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">北京广播电视台、北京时间精心制作，微信视频号独家直播的</span>“点燃希望--2023中国经济十大预测”——</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">泽平宏观视频号观看量超630万</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">，微信生态内曝光量6000万+</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">，台网累计超1000万观看，二次传播5.5亿+，多条观点登上热搜。</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;text-align: justify;margin: 10px 0px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration: none solid rgb(0, 0, 0);">2023年7月15日，任泽平年中秀: 点燃希望一中国经济十大新机遇，与北京电视台、苏州市文旅联合举办。首次启用线上+线下模式，2500位企业家级用户齐聚苏州，2000万在线观看，今日头条热榜前五，全流程触达人次约5亿。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">知识教育、商学院、品牌商务、股权投资等各项业务持续快速增长。</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;text-align: justify;margin: 10px 0px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration: none solid rgb(0, 0, 0);">2023年，泽平宏观·实战研学已开展了11站精彩的标杆企业访学。每月任泽平博士带领企业家学员们去企业开拓视野、学习企业经营之道与创新实践、探寻新机遇。在过往访学中，学员们走进了华为、新希望、茅台、东方甄选、360集团、蔚来汽车、字节跳动、科大讯飞、元气森林、名创优品、广汽埃安等等科技旗舰企业总部基地、行业龙头企业与创始人们交流学习。</span><strong style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">公司凭借高端专业口碑，与政府部门、行业协会、金融机构、大型企业等均建立长期良好的合作关系，如全国工商联、北京广播电视台、茅台集团、洋河股份、腾讯集团、联想集团、百度、阿里、飞鹤、蔚来汽车、抖音等机构，打造“点燃希望”年度演讲大秀、大咖会客厅等多档优质知名产品，获得广泛好评和大奖。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">由经济学家任泽平博士联合携程创始人梁建章先生等共同发起成立育娲人口公益研究机构。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">泽平宏观研发的专业财经课程在各大平台广受欢迎。</span></p><p><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">员工中博士及硕士学历占比超过70%，汇聚了来自全球各大名校的人才。</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">……</span></p><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,